table></div><br /><br /><b>IVC</b> <br /><ul><li>Commences at vertebral level T8 </li><li>Ends by bifurcating below the aorta at L5 level. </li></ul><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/fti223b.png'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/fti223.png'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'></td><td align='right'></td></tr></table></CENTER><div class='imagetext'>Diagram illustrating the abdominal aorta & IVC</div><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/swb139b.png'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/swb139.png'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>Image sourced from </span><a href='http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/diaphragm'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >Wikipedia</a></td><td align='right'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox lbmagglasslink' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/swb139b.png'><img src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/css/images/mag_glass.png'/></a></td></tr></table></CENTER><div class='imagetext'>Diagram illustrating the abdominal aorta branches</div><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/swb140b.jpg'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/swb140.jpg'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>Image sourced from </span><a href='http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/diaphragm'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >Wikipedia</a></td><td align='rig